  "detailed_description": "<strong>Limited Lifetime Corp</strong> is a day by day management sim.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Harvest Resources</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/89328a83fa6f171ff3ef51f14bbf6e96.poster.avif?t=1685305845\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/89328a83fa6f171ff3ef51f14bbf6e96.webm?t=1685305845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/89328a83fa6f171ff3ef51f14bbf6e96.mp4?t=1685305845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Deploy your excavators to multiple regions to gather resources. As your <strong>LLC</strong> grows, you can expand to many more regions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beware the Local Fauna</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/5729473963ad14d8b6ed1dddb897bf21.poster.avif?t=1685305845\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/5729473963ad14d8b6ed1dddb897bf21.webm?t=1685305845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/5729473963ad14d8b6ed1dddb897bf21.mp4?t=1685305845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Keep an eye on the shifting sands for any unwanted guests. <br>You can't be everywhere, so you can deploy automated lookouts to warn of you impending dangers, both real and imaginary.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Profit</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/f4dff3fa82a66aa891a6c9116bf12322.poster.avif?t=1685305845\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/f4dff3fa82a66aa891a6c9116bf12322.webm?t=1685305845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/f4dff3fa82a66aa891a6c9116bf12322.mp4?t=1685305845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>At the end of the day, you receive the fruits of your labor. You can purchase more machines, upgrade them, and purchase more land rights.<br>But be warned, there are those jealous of your profits.<br><br>How Long Can Your <strong>LLC</strong> Survive?",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Limited Lifetime Corp</strong> is a day by day management sim.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Harvest Resources</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/89328a83fa6f171ff3ef51f14bbf6e96.poster.avif?t=1685305845\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/89328a83fa6f171ff3ef51f14bbf6e96.webm?t=1685305845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/89328a83fa6f171ff3ef51f14bbf6e96.mp4?t=1685305845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Deploy your excavators to multiple regions to gather resources. As your <strong>LLC</strong> grows, you can expand to many more regions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beware the Local Fauna</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/5729473963ad14d8b6ed1dddb897bf21.poster.avif?t=1685305845\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/5729473963ad14d8b6ed1dddb897bf21.webm?t=1685305845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/5729473963ad14d8b6ed1dddb897bf21.mp4?t=1685305845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Keep an eye on the shifting sands for any unwanted guests. <br>You can't be everywhere, so you can deploy automated lookouts to warn of you impending dangers, both real and imaginary.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Profit</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/f4dff3fa82a66aa891a6c9116bf12322.poster.avif?t=1685305845\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/f4dff3fa82a66aa891a6c9116bf12322.webm?t=1685305845\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2055720/extras/f4dff3fa82a66aa891a6c9116bf12322.mp4?t=1685305845\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>At the end of the day, you receive the fruits of your labor. You can purchase more machines, upgrade them, and purchase more land rights.<br>But be warned, there are those jealous of your profits.<br><br>How Long Can Your <strong>LLC</strong> Survive?",
